  "texts": [
    "As Max silently made their way out of the room, a sudden commotion erupted.",
    "The Phoenix members became aware of the planted devices and realized they were under surveillance.",
    "Panic filled the air as they quickly evacuated the premises.",
    "Max's heart sank.",
    "Outside the meeting room, Max's mind raced trying to make sense of the situation."
